		<content type="html">&lt;p&gt;It has been a while after I tried to build a webpage myself. The reason why I didn&#x27;t explore this area is simply because building a webpage takes quite an efforts to learn and implement and obviously, time is not on my side. &lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Testing a python code block&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
